name: Portal of Space - Galactibles™ #09
description: Snap dragons, it’s a portal! You've discovered Galactible™ #09, the mysterious "Portal of Space!" Harness this Galactible™ to summon a portal on any world! Where will it take you? Jump through and find out! Your Mana has been raised by +45,000 bits! Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Chilly vibes and original music produced by DRMCRSHR (linktr.ee/drmcrshr)!!!
